WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.408 --> 00:00:16.235
<b>It was holiday time. Veena and
Vinay were in the garden.</b>

2
00:00:17.626 --> 00:00:21.009
<b>There were tins of
paint everywhere.</b>

3
00:00:23.173 --> 00:00:32.314
<b>There was white paint and red paint and green
paint and blue paint and yellow paint.</b>

4
00:00:32.540 --> 00:00:34.571
<b>The painters were busy.</b>

5
00:00:36.017 --> 00:00:38.626
<b>One painter was on a ladder.</b>

6
00:00:39.829 --> 00:00:43.767
<b>Another was hanging from
the roof on a swing.</b>

7
00:00:46.119 --> 00:00:50.009
<b>Can we help? asked
Veena and Vinay.</b>

8
00:00:50.407 --> 00:00:54.251
<b>The painter gave each
of them a brush.</b>

9
00:00:54.478 --> 00:00:58.298
<b>Paint the inside of the
gate, he said to Veena.</b>

10
00:01:00.071 --> 00:01:04.134
<b>Paint the outside of the
gate, he said to Vinay.</b>

11
00:01:06.158 --> 00:01:10.603
<b>They picked up two tins
of paint and set to work.</b>

12
00:01:12.174 --> 00:01:14.993
<b>Veena painted one
side of the gate.</b>

13
00:01:16.548 --> 00:01:19.868
<b>Vinay painted the other
side of the gate.</b>

14
00:01:22.095 --> 00:01:29.790
<b>The paint fell on the ground. The paint
fell on the wall. The paint fell on them.</b>

15
00:01:30.141 --> 00:01:32.798
<b>At last they finished.</b>

16
00:01:33.095 --> 00:01:36.782
<b>They wiped off the paint that
had splashed on the ground.</b>

17
00:01:38.133 --> 00:01:41.540
<b>They wiped off the paint that
had splashed on the wall.</b>

18
00:01:43.297 --> 00:01:46.571
<b>They wiped off the paint
that had splashed on them.</b>

19
00:01:48.001 --> 00:01:52.087
<b>I love my red gate! said Veena.</b>

20
00:01:53.119 --> 00:01:57.290
<b>I love my green gate! said Vinay.</b>

21
00:02:00.048 --> 00:02:06.689
<b>Oh, you have made a two-coloured gate!
cried the painter.</b>

22
00:02:06.924 --> 00:02:10.375
<b>Let us keep it that way!
said Mother.</b>

